            "title": "盤中速報 - 巨騰-DR(9136)股價殺至跌停，跌停價9.86元，成交1,874張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>巨騰-DR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9136:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9136\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9136-TW</a>)27日09:51下跌1.09元，股價跌停報9.86元，委買66張、委賣1張，成交1,874張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為生產及銷售筆記本型電腦外殼。生產及銷售手持設備外殼。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>巨騰-DR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9136:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9136\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9136-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲8.96%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.05%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,350 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,350 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,502 張</li> <li>融券增減：+475 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
