            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>燿華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2367:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2367\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2367-TW</a>)27日09:53股價上漲5.3元，報80.6元，漲幅7.04%，成交122,591張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>燿華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2367:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2367\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2367-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為印刷電路板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.44%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.05%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+3,933 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+6,777 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-28 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-2,816 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,418 張</li> <li>融券增減：+904 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
